cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DS, cs.PL

This paper discusses the need for balancing openness and privacy in cloud systems, which is a security and privacy concern (cs.CR). It also focuses on the utilization and performance of physical infrastructure, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses technical challenges and possibilities, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses the implications of transparency for cloud systems and users, which is related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and programming languages (cs.PL).
